winget-gui-tui
==============

This project is a from-scratch C# / Terminal.Gui v2 reimplementation of:

    shanselman/winget-tui
    https://github.com/shanselman/winget-tui
    Copyright (c) Scott Hanselman
    Licensed under the MIT License

The upstream Rust + Ratatui app was used as the behavioral and visual
specification while writing this port. UI layout, keybindings, color
palette, status bar, table layout, parsing strategy, dedupe logic, and the
"Found <name> [<id>]" header convention were all studied directly from
upstream source.

This is an independent rewrite — no upstream code was copied — but the
specification debt is acknowledged. See feature-gaps.md for an audit of
behavioral differences between the two implementations.

This project's own license is MIT (see LICENSE).
